settings.heading: The best Sofa I've ever had!
settings.text:
I purchased the "Rupert" range and I can honestly say it's the best Sofa I've ever had! And I've had many! From the classic elegant look, to the luxury feel and comfort, I often get asked about it, everyone loves it when they visit, Also the service and extremely quick delivery from Honeypot was 2nd to none! I highly recommend this company and their fabulous furniture, 5 stars from me!

Teena - View Instagram

settings.heading: Inga sofa - highly recommend!
settings.text:
First time using Honeypot furniture and I would highly recommend! We ordered the Inga sofa in cream. The delivery service was great - the delivery men carried the sofa to our front room and helped set up the sofa. The sofa is super comfy and exactly how the photo looked on the website. We often spend most Sundays relaxing on the sofa and we couldn’t be any more happier with it!

Georgia - View Instagram

settings.heading: Beautiful sofa!
settings.text:
Beautifully made U shaped bishop sofa was purchased online from this small family run business - excellent communication from start to finish and useful delivery updates on the day to make this a hassle free purchase - highly recommended!

Lesley
